  "text": "In general, explicit evaluations of Gauss sums are very difficult. There are only a few cases where the Gauss sums have been evaluated, see [CITATION_1] for known results on Gauss sums. In Section 4, we will use the explicit evaluations of Gauss sums of the quadratic residue case and index 2 case. ",
